review_blob: Very unusual porter. It has a subtle chocolate taste, a hint of coffee bean but a smooth finish. Very drinkable.
Nice, better than the standard Tooheys.
One of the very, very best.
I enjoy this beer, although it is over carbonated. The taste is much better than Toohey's Blue or Red or New...
I had to rate all these beers at once because theyre so fantastic! I love the texture and the flavour. This beer has a lot more boldness to it than the others.
Not quite as powerful as the Macedon ale but it is a very tasty beer. The flavour is second to none while the appearance is outstanding.
One of the best beers I have ever tasted. The aroma is tantilizing, and the flavour has depth and power. I highly recommend this outstanding beer.
